<% content_for(:title, "MK Web development") %>

<div class="post">
	<div class="post_title" style="font-family:'Lato'; font-weight:900; font-size: 3em; line-height: 0.6;">MY FIRST POST TITLE TEXT <br /><span style="font-weight:100; font-size:0.5em;">Release date: 20.06.2014</span></div>
	<br />
	<div class="short_desc" style="font-family:'Lato'; font-weight:300; font-size: 1.4em;"><p>This is my text short description, it's my first short description so be full of empathy, because apparently I need a lot of it my simple, one cocked friend. Here I'm going to tell you 10 reasons to follow your dreams:
		<br />
